{"tid":875073,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"投資者連環沽貨　減價近百萬出售新葵芳花園","createTime":"2018-10-24T16:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T01:59:40.000Z","uid":174649,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"135ffa6d3e154996c932c3296b32455e40c62c07","tid":875073,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181024/photo/bkn-20181024223442794-1024_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181024234230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181024%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181024223442794-1024_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181024234230&h=5f5bf98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中原許偉業表示，市況逆轉，葵涌區有投資者最近持續減持物業，不惜以低價沽貨，區內小業主持貨信心受挫，紛紛減價求售，部分業主轉賣為租，甚至封盤。<br />\n<br />\n許偉業表示，新葵芳花園B座中層3室，實用面積408方呎，兩房間隔，業主於區內持有多伙物業，外區亦有物業，見市況持續轉差，樓價有下行壓力，決定減磅止賺離場，上月中叫價720萬元放售，本月中降價至680萬元，近日進一步減至624萬元沽出，呎價15,294元，減幅達13%。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該投資者最近持續減磅，日前售出屋苑B座高層4室，實用面積400方呎，成交價629.8萬元，較銀行估價低約8%。"},{"pid":"0964d7315cd75a1150a1eef652ced8d1c1b82054","tid":875073,"uid":42921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"部分業主轉賣為租，甚至封盤<br />\n<br />\n升唔賣，跌唔賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc46a4bac3ed48b86351854835266b790ef53ae2","tid":875073,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"新葵之前可以賣到700萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b1bca0b9dd41f202f78ee3335501c4aadc07db","tid":875073,"uid":176681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"樓市幾時懲罰投資者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bb481e0c6b4277f1d57a8fe3cb81d9e4